TEXT.S: Eddie Biedenbach nalecuhan i Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania, nanu syubay kanas-mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, pahanhanan tu kawaw ayza. Eddie Biedenbach i 1968 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 4 ku uwac atu silsil 45, namapili' tu nu Los Angeles Lakers putiput. tatama, nalecuhan i 8 a bulad 12 a demiad, 1945 a mihcan, Eddie Biedenbach, miunduay.
